data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4BR, 4BA home nestled in The Glen at Widefield. A classic covered front porch provides an inviting welcome to a light & bright open floor plan that's awaiting you behind the front door! Inside, you'll find a well-appointed living space that's both comfortable & functional. Central air & heat for year round comfort. Sec system for added protection. Gorgeous wood floors through the Kitchen, Dining Area, & Living Rm. The tiled Entry has stairs to the UL & leads you into a front office that features neutral carpet & lots of natural light. There is a Powder Bathroom for guests. The Island Kitchen is a chef's delight & boasts a walk in pantry, wine cellar fridge, counter bar w/ pendant lights, & cabinets w/ beautiful granite countertops for storage & easy food preparation. SS appl incl a smooth top range oven, microwave, dishwasher, & side by side refrigerator. The Dining Area has a walk out to the backyard deck. The Living Rm offers a lighted ceiling fan, an art & TV recess, built-in shelves, & a gas log fireplace w/ stone surround to cozy up to on chilly winter nights. Upstairs, you'll find a Laundry Rm w/ washer & dryer that stays, a versatile loft & 3 spacious BRs that offer comfort & privacy, with the primary bedroom featuring a 5pc en-suite bathroom & walk in closet for added convenience. 2 more bedrooms with walk in closets share a full hall bathroom w/ vanity, mirror, & tub/shower. The Walk Out Basement provides a huge Family/Rec Rm w/ under stair storage that can serve many purposes such as a Family Rm, Theater Rm, Gym, or Play Rm. There is a 4th BR & full bathroom, perfect for guests or in-laws. 3-car attached garage. The fenced lot offers a deck w/ stairs to the backyard for outdoor relaxation & fun. The neighborhood offers trails & a tranquil pond nearby. It is a quick commute to Fort Carson & minutes to shopping & entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this amazing home your own – a delightful mix of comfort and style.
